{"type":"message","id":"8aff86b8","parentId":"df79e9a5","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:10:22.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Context is at 72%, which exceeds the 60% threshold. The script is suggesting to start a new session. Let me check what's currently in context and see if there's anything that can be summarized or cleared before suggesting a new session.\n\nActually, the context monitor has already done its job - it's alerted that context is at 72%. According to my instructions, I should be proactive here. Let me think about what's reasonable:\n\n1. The context is at 72% - not critical yet but heading there\n2. I could check if there's any low-value content that could be summarized/cleared\n3. Or I could just note this and continue - 72% is still workable\n\nLet me check the current session status to understand what's using context, then decide if action is needed.","thinkingSignature":"0d2de2be4d588ec35599b5a70f2fa4d7ddcdb2c79a91d90df333f14f6e576536"},{"type":"text","text":"Context 使用率 72%，超过 60% 阈值。让我检查当前会话状态，看看是否有可清理的内容：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j4b0wyn9mehp_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":451,"output":201,"cacheRead":38931,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39583,"cost":{"input":0.00013529999999999998,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00116793,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0015444299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774073415093}}
